imgui.ini

# =================================
# Library Files (.lib / .dll)
# =================================
# Abaikan .lib hasil compile sendiri
*.lib
*.dll
*.exe

# PENGECUALIAN:
# Jika kamu punya file .lib mentahan (Pre-built) yang WAJIB ada di folder External,
# hapus tanda pagar (#) di baris bawah ini:
# !External/**/*.lib
# !External/**/*.dll